<h3>Information about the Stop Smoking module</h3>
<p>If you are worried about the impact smoking is having on your health, quitting is one of the most effective steps you can take to improve your health.</p>
<p>If you are not sure where to start with quitting, here are some practical ideas to help you...</p>
<p>When you decide to stop smoking you don't have to do it alone. <a href="http://www.stopsmokingwales.com/" target="_blank">Stop Smoking Wales</a> is a free NHS service to help people in Wales quit smoking.</p>
<p>Giving up smoking isn't easy, so Stop Smoking Wales offers a friendly group approach to help you to quit smoking and stay smoke-free.</p>
<p>You are <strong>four times more likely to quit</strong> with a support programme like Stop Smoking Wales than going it alone. </p>
<p>You can find out more about the <a href="http://www.stopsmokingwales.com/how-the-service-works" target="_blank">how the Stop Smoking Wales service works</a> and look at the <a href="http://www.stopsmokingwales.com/they-did-it-so-can-you" target="_blank">case studies</a> to find out how real people have found the service.</p>
<p>Worried about cravings and putting on weight? Visit the <a href="http://www.nhs.uk/Pages/HomePage.aspx" target="_blank">NHS Choices</a> website to find out more information about how to cope with <a href="http://www.nhs.uk/Livewell/smoking/Pages/Copingwithcravings.aspx" target="_blank">cravings</a> and <a href="http://www.nhs.uk/Livewell/smoking/Pages/weightgain.aspx" target="_blank">avoid putting on weight</a> while quitting smoking.</p>
<p>Need some simple tips on helping you quit? <a href="http://www.stopsmokingwales.com/top-tips-to-quit" target="_blank">Read top tips to quit</a> by Stop Smoking Wales.</p>
<p>Looking at your smoking pattern, can help you <a href="http://www.stopsmokingwales.com/what-is-your-smoking-pattern" target="_blank">plan for your quit attempt</a> by recognising the cigarettes which will be the most difficult to give-up.</p>
